      "body": "> While OSS-Fuzz does cover leveldb (https://github.com/google/oss-fuzz/blob/master/projects/leveldb/fuzz_db.cc), it ...\r\n\r\nI wouldn't put too much value in this. I think there is only a single fuzz target, which fails, according to https://issues.oss-fuzz.com/issues/447252244, so it may be unmaintained. \r\n\r\n<!--\r\n\r\n> TSan\r\n\r\nReminds me that we didn't have any multi-threaded test in the past, so there is no TSan fuzz CI config. Could make sense to consider adding one at some point?",
